title: Kat Graham Attends Variety And Women In Film Annual Pre-Emmy Celebration, 2015 Entertainment Weekly Pre-Emmy Party
content:
View image | gettyimages.com West Hollywood, California - Twenty six year old actress Kat Graham looked fabulous wearing a green strapless dress with heels as she stepped out to attend Variety And Women In Film Annual Pre-Emmy Celebration held at Gracias Madre and 2015 Entertainment Weekly Pre-Emmy Party  at Fig & Olive on Saturday, September 18th, 2015 in West Hollywood, California.
Katerina Alexandre Hartford "Kat" Graham is a Swiss-born American actress, model, singer and dancer. She is known for her role of Bonnie Bennett on The CW supernatural drama The Vampire Diaries.
